title: Teams We Should “Stick a Fork” In & TNF Preview
itunes:title: Teams We Should “Stick a Fork” In & TNF Preview
description:
A room filled with heroes - Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal, Chris Wesseling and Marc Sessler – break down Matt Ryan leading the Falcons to a win in the Super Dome over the Saints on Monday Night Football. Then, the guys reveal which teams have no shot to make the 2016 playoffs and preview the Thursday Night Football Bengals-Dolphins match up. Also, the heroes welcome a surprise guest to help decide who should be the “Team of ATL” for the 2016 season before saying goodbye to the Irishman on his last show.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
